{"tid":221170,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有果食經驗?","createTime":"2017-04-28T13:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T13:45:12.000Z","uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91dd237eeb4f318126fce94cd569e0b85107f81b","tid":221170,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"而家香港地一日3餐出街食好撚貴... 一日都舊幾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果全日都食水果，我估3,40蚊都食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間都慳唔少，有無巴絲有相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d7169575466731d6c475e4a6c2ef84c57f5d6b","tid":221170,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"三餐食會糖尿病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd5d05a448f3d0ffd6d2f8c847edc16aaa3d378","tid":221170,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"糖尿病患者食唔食得水果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f6854988771e7d4f8be03619b119b2fa591853","tid":221170,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"食咩先飽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00e0747837c2617b6d99e16f52ae193de3e9bb7","tid":221170,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:59:18.000Z","msg":"食兩條蕉都飽死"},{"pid":"810dce55ed0ed84f5c6a6c923cb5213ca7362c7a","tid":221170,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食兩條蕉都飽死</blockquote><br />\n如果食兩條蕉你都飽死，咁你食兩個雞尾包都足夠你飽死有突。咁又何來你開post所講每餐要三四十蚊，所以要轉食生果？<br />\n無邏輯思維就會成日郁下就自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d917fb789b9061eee9b3e63e554b56b5519e2db9","tid":221170,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果全日都食水果，我估3,40蚊都食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間都慳唔少，有無巴絲有相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實全果食，洗費貴過食肉，<br />\n你想慳錢慳時間就唔洗諗喇"},{"pid":"c9e59d549aa7bd8116869df1d85949e7ad91307e","tid":221170,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食兩條蕉都飽死</blockquote><br />\n如果食兩條蕉你都飽死，咁你食兩個雞尾包都足夠你飽死有突。咁又何來你開post所講每餐要三四十蚊，所以要轉食生果？<br />\n無邏輯思維就會成日郁下就自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純睇錢你不如話食垃圾，贏緊呀你"},{"pid":"4ae8ba6c902730bad00a144abd2ab6ab1291e6c9","tid":221170,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果全日都食水果，我估3,40蚊都食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間都慳唔少，有無巴絲有相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實全果食，洗費貴過食肉，<br />\n你想慳錢慳時間就唔洗諗喇</blockquote><br />\n試個一日有一兩餐食生果，要搵10蚊/15蚊一盤先會平，夠飽肚，如果買貴既生果真係貴過食肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d644f3f1baf14ba73e0d81a9c0b20eaf3d88fc1","tid":221170,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"會糖尿病，不了。"}]}